Hmmm..... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/ustaby.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Staby</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Pre-Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(7/18/02 9:03:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1762.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   no expert</span><hr size=1> Heh its not going to be done professionally beucase I am not a professional, nor anything close to a great 3d modeler. Just want to try my best but not just make it for myself, but for other as well. One reason I am not adding voice actors is one, i have none, two takes up a lot of space that can be replaced with music &amp; more detailed graphics. anyways it supose to be a learning exp. So i am calling it a night and going to sleep. hope to hear more responces <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/uoursinis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>OurSin Is</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(7/19/02 12:46:06 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1762.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Key pointing in interest of Anime?</span><hr size=1> Both.....good story line + good action = good stuff<br>
